# Bulk MgZn2 single point energy

units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary p p p

read_data bulk_structure/mgzn2_relaxed.data

pair_style meam
pair_coeff * * library.meam Zn Mg ZnMg.meam Mg Zn

thermo 1
thermo_style custom step pe etotal press vol
fix 1 all box/relax x 0.0 y 0.0 couple none
minimize 1e-8 1e-8 10000 100000
run 0
